/blockquote><br />\n所以我估下次23條立法前會搞件大粒嘢，唔通係68.............<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520128991e59547f6f9d7225704dda193b2c0a08","tid":502831,"uid":22387,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"佢呢d case入到去實成班警犬幫住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31dec147b651dcea4eebf6b2511097b8e7d8874","tid":502831,"uid":33050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>伙記 嚟個朱經緯套餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb099163b4897d4b8ec6fd92c3a42e37aafeda4","tid":502831,"uid":31405,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"做咩扮晒死狗無晒火咁款？<br />\n之前唔係好型架咩？<br />\n<br />\n出黎打鳩d香港人啦！屌你老母"},{"pid":"96a342259200907c5fd54095275d1a96cd46e1ea","tid":502831,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:54:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無限資源<br />\n一定打到去終審<br />\n終審時自然找到借口，判無罪<br />\n<br />\n香港法治已死</blockquote><br />\n都已經搞到佢一輪，坐左一輪監"},{"pid":"e6370b59e25619c4c2098bfbfc670488b91aa6ac","tid":502831,"uid":9732,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:54:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾蘋果訪問竟然冇發爛渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人之將死 其言也善  <br />\n<br />\n唔記得句嘢係咪咁"},{"pid":"4f157a0bb1494a3fa61a7d3e94c68ac0aa3b5e67","tid":502831,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171218/large/1513590239_9447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%